      p Smartphones are powerful tools. With the device in our pocket, we can communicate with millions of people, take photos, and access nearly all the information known to man. But since the advent of these devices, people aren't getting closer. If anything, we're getting further apart.
      p The average person spends four hours of their life using their smartphones, time that they could be spending with people, or doing more useful things.
